<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="78" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,389,2033]" pageId="12" pageNumber="78">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,308,1901,1925]" pageId="12" pageNumber="78">Remarks</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName box="[323,653,1901,1925]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Acyphoderes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="78" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="sensu" subSpecies="auctorum">
<emphasis box="[323,653,1901,1925]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="78">Acyphoderes sensu auctorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
encompasses more than one genus. The new species here described, without doubt, is not a true 
<taxonomicName box="[460,603,1937,1961]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Acyphoderes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="78" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[460,603,1937,1961]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="78">Acyphoderes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Although, we know that Robin O. S. Clarke (personal communication) is working on a revision of this genus, we do not know how long this will take. Thus, we are describing provisionally the species in 
<taxonomicName box="[308,452,2009,2033]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Acyphoderes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="78" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[308,452,2009,2033]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="78">Acyphoderes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
